
Ranger Help for: enemy cat
==========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing cat means your Ranger hunts feline predators: wildcats, lions,
panthers, jaguars, and similar stalking beasts.

This is a strong choice for forests, jungles, hills, and mountains. It
represents a Ranger who knows how ambush predators move, hide, and spring.

COMMAND:
  setenemy cat

=============================================================================
